Harcourt Brace Jovanovich Incsaid it sold 4,805,432 shares of its common at 10.25 dlrs ashare to an employee stock ownership plan as part of itspreviously announced recapitalization plan.    Harcourt said the shares sold are not entitled to a specialdividend previously declared under the plan. It said the shareswill be entitled to vote at a special meeting of shareholdersscheduled for July 23. Reuter&#3;